## Running Commands

Run scripts via `uv run <script>`. Available project scripts: `uv run pytest`, `uv run ruff`, `uv run mypy`.

Non-bash scripts run with `uv run scripts/<script-name>`. Bash scripts run with `bash scripts/<script-name>`.

For string interpolation, heredocs, loops, or advanced xargs flags, write a script in `scripts/` instead.

Use `curl` when you need to see the full response content (WebFetch summarizes).
